data.description: Price Adjustment! This 3BR/2Ba 1416 sq ft home with additional BR and full Ba in guesthouse overlooks the hillside making this home a unique find! The kitchen and living room are open with gorgeous oak cabinetry. The upper level has large master bed and bath with walk in closet. Large, covered front porch perfect for sipping morning coffee. The guest house is close behind main connected by a walkway and covered back stoop.The property includes 18.45 scenic acres teaming with wildlife in a stand of mature timber. Perfect for the nature lover looking for a private area, yet within minutes from the amenities of town. Property also has a workshop with attached carports that has electric, a 5x10 concrete storm shelter, an 8x8 greenhouse, a grilling and picnic area, a circle drive with gated entries
